On this page
Getting Started
Welcome to 
â€‹
This script allows you to create your own scripts without any programming, using simple building blocks that you arrange.
Before you get started, you may want to go through the Guides (
Scripts
is a great place to start!) to get a better understanding of how 
When you first launch the script, you can press the
Script Network
button and download a script or two to see how they're made.
For more thorough examples you can also check out
Tutorials
for tutorials or the
#scripts
forum for user created scripts in our
Discord server
.
You can also find common questions and their answers on the
FAQ page
, and if you're ever stuck be sure to ask for help in our
Discord server
.
You can also find
all available actions
and see their parameters and any other relevant helpful tips.
Good luck and have fun!
